Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: Golden Gate Bridge
Description: This suspension bridge is not only known as an icon of SF Bay, but is now also a "giant orange wheezing kazoo."

Name: Japantown, SF
Description: A wonderful historic neighborhood celebrating Japanese culture.

Name: Rockaway Beach
Description: A popular beach in Pacifica showcasing sand and a hikeable hill where you can see all of Pacifica.

Name: CA Academy of Sciences
Description: A research institute and one of the largest natural history museums in the world - the planetarium is my favorite exhibit.

Name: Coal Oil Point
Description: A beach west of UCSB that is another great place to watch the sunset after classes.
